'''瓦濟里斯坦'''(普什圖語和{{lang-ur|وزیرستان}})，又譯'''瓦澤爾斯坦、瓦齊里斯坦'''，是一个多山地区，涵蓋[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[北瓦济里斯坦特区|北瓦济里斯坦特区]]和[[南瓦济里斯坦特区|南瓦濟里斯坦特區]]兩個前[[联邦直辖部落地区|联邦直辖部落地区]]；这两个地区现在都是[[开伯尔-普什图省|开伯尔─普赫图赫瓦省]]的辖区。<ref>{{Cite web|title=President signs constitutional amendment to merge FATA with KP|url=https://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2018/05/31/president-signs-constitutional-amendment-to-merge-fata-with-kp/|accessdate=2018-06-28|work=www.pakistantoday.com.pk|language=en-GB|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127024504/https://www.pakistantoday.com.pk/2018/05/31/president-signs-constitutional-amendment-to-merge-fata-with-kp/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1416536|title=KP plans to take control of Fata health directorate|author=Yusufzai|first=Ashfaq|date=28 June 2018|work=DAWN.COM|accessdate=2018-06-28|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210815085644/https://www.dawn.com/news/1416536|dead-url=no}}</ref> 瓦濟里斯坦占地约11,585平方公里(4,500平方英里)。該地區居住普什图人。地區因瓦濟里部落而得名。<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Tribe: Ahmadzai Wazir|url=http://www.nps.edu/programs/ccs/Docs/Pakistan/Tribes/Ahmadzai_Wazir.pdf|publisher=Naval Postgraduate School|journal=|access-date=2021-09-10|archive-date=2014-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104081830/http://www.nps.edu/programs/ccs/Docs/Pakistan/Tribes/Ahmadzai_Wazir.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 主要語言是屬於普什圖語的瓦濟里方言。

16世纪的[[普什图|普什图]]革命领袖、战士诗人巴亚兹德 · 皮尔 · 罗山(Bayazid Pir Roshan)以瓦濟里斯坦的{{Link-en|加尼古勒姆|Kaniguram}}为本，写出了普什圖最古老、最知名的作品。

== 概述和历史 ==
[[File:FATA_(8).jpg|替代=]]和省份的]]
瓦濟里斯坦位于北面的[[托奇河|托奇河]]和南面的[[古馬勒河|古馬勒河]]之间。东北緊鄰[[本努县|本努]]和[[坦克市|坦克市]]、[[德拉伊斯梅尔汗边疆区|德拉伊斯梅爾汗邊疆區]]和[[古勒姆特区|古勒姆特区]]，南部与[[俾路支省|俾路支]]的{{Translink|en|sherani|謝拉尼}}和[[穆萨克尔县|穆萨赫尔縣]]接壤，西北接壤[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]的[[帕克蒂卡省|帕克蒂卡省]]、[[霍斯特|霍斯特省]]、[[帕克蒂亚省|帕克蒂亞省]]。

瓦濟里斯坦分为[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[开伯尔-普什图省|开伯尔─普赫图赫瓦省]]北瓦济里斯坦特区和南瓦濟里斯坦特區。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1416536|title=KP plans to take control of Fata health directorate|author=Yusufzai|first=Ashfaq|date=28 June 2018|work=DAWN.COM|accessdate=2018-06-28|language=en-US}}</ref> 根据2017年巴基斯坦人口普查，北瓦济里斯坦特区的人口为543,254<ref>{{Cite web|title=DISTRICT AND TEHSIL LEVEL POPULATION SUMMARY WITH REGION BREAKUP - North Waziristan|url=http://www.pbscensus.gov.pk/sites/default/files/bwpsr/fata/NOR_WAZIRISTAN_AGENCY_SUMMARY.pdf|accessdate=2018-06-28|work=www.pbscensus.gov.pk|archive-date=2018-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180326141546/http://www.pbscensus.gov.pk/sites/default/files/bwpsr/fata/NOR_WAZIRISTAN_AGENCY_SUMMARY.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，而南瓦濟里斯坦特區的人口为674,065。<ref>{{Cite web|title=DISTRICT AND TEHSIL LEVEL POPULATION SUMMARY WITH REGION BREAKUP - South Waziristan|url=http://www.pbscensus.gov.pk/sites/default/files/bwpsr/fata/SOUTH_WAZIRISTAN_AGENCY_SUMMARY.pdf|accessdate=2018-06-28|work=www.pbscensus.gov.pk|archive-date=2018-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180326141531/http://www.pbscensus.gov.pk/sites/default/files/bwpsr/fata/SOUTH_WAZIRISTAN_AGENCY_SUMMARY.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 儘管一樣是瓦濟里部落，兩個區有著不同的特色。 他们被认为是令人敬畏的战士。<ref>"A powerful tribal chief has warned militants linked with al-Qaeda to leave a Pakistani border district after the death of eight members of his clan supporting peace efforts in the troubled region. [[Maulvi_Nazir|Maulavi Nazir]], who drove out hundreds of [[Uzbeks|Uzbek]] fighters in a bloody battle last year, said his armed followers would attack those loyal to an al-Qaeda linchpin in South Waziristan. Mr Nazir, who represents the influential Wazir tribe, blamed Baitullah Mehsud..."  (Australian News Network), 8 January 2008 ([http://backroadsbubba.newsvine.com/_news/2008/01/09/1213546-tribal-chief-tells-militants-to-leave on-line] {{Wayback|url=http://backroadsbubba.newsvine.com/_news/2008/01/09/1213546-tribal-chief-tells-militants-to-leave |date=20110714174658 }})</ref>

1894年，[[英国人|英国人]]进入瓦濟里斯坦，沿著[[杜兰线|杜蘭線]]與[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]分鄰。<ref>Chisholm, Hugh, ed. (1911). "Waziristan" . Encyclopædia Britannica. 28 (11th ed.). Cambridge University Press. pp. 9.</ref> [[英国|英国]]将瓦濟里斯坦分为北瓦濟里斯坦和南瓦濟里斯坦。北瓦濟里斯坦，首府設米蘭夏(Miramshah)；南瓦濟里斯坦，首府設在[[瓦納_(巴基斯坦)|瓦納]] 。

1919年，[[第三次英国－阿富汗战争|英阿戰爭]]中，阿富汗入侵英屬印度。1919至1920年間的瓦濟里斯坦起義相呼而起。最終，英軍順利平定起義。

1935年至1936年間，由人稱伊平的法基爾的{{Tsl|en|Mirzali Khan|米爾扎利汗}}發起新的起義。游擊戰一路延燒到戰後。1938年，{{Tsl|en|Mirzali Khan|米爾扎利汗}}在古尔韦克（Gurwek）宣布獨立。1947年6月，米爾扎利汗與運動(Khudai Khidmatgars)成員達成普什圖斯坦決議，要求英國政府让普什圖人拥有一個独立的普什圖斯坦，而不是让他们加入巴基斯坦。然而，英国拒绝这项决议。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=c05uAAAAMAAJ|title=Afghanistan and the Frontier|last=Ali Shah|first=Sayyid Vaqar|date=1993|publisher=Emjay Books International|editor-last=Marwat|editor-first=Fazal-ur-Rahim Khan|location=University of Michigan|page=256|access-date=2021-09-10|archive-date=2019-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219182034/https://books.google.com/books?id=c05uAAAAMAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=B9ZZAgAAQBAJ|title=Culture, Conflict, and Counterinsurgency|last=H Johnson|first=Thomas|last2=Zellen|first2=Barry|date=2014|publisher=[[Stanford_University_Press|Stanford University Press]]|isbn=9780804789219|page=154|authorlink=Thomas Howard Johnson|access-date=2021-09-10|archive-date=2019-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191219182407/https://books.google.com/books?id=B9ZZAgAAQBAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref> 1947年8月巴基斯坦建国后，米尔扎利汗及其追随者拒绝承认巴基斯坦，并发动了针对巴基斯坦的游击战。<ref>[https://tribune.com.pk/story/77388/the-faqir-of-ipi-of-north-waziristan/ The Faqir of Ipi of North Waziristan] {{Wayback|url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/77388/the-faqir-of-ipi-of-north-waziristan/ |date=20190416231409 }}. ''[[The_Express_Tribune|The Express Tribune]]''. 15 November 2010.</ref> 1960年，米爾札利汗在古尔韦克去世。<ref>[https://tribune.com.pk/story/1086737/april-1891-1960-the-legendary-guerilla-faqir-of-ipi-unremembered-on-his-115th-anniversary/ The legendary guerilla Faqir of Ipi unremembered on his 115th anniversary] {{Wayback|url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/1086737/april-1891-1960-the-legendary-guerilla-faqir-of-ipi-unremembered-on-his-115th-anniversary/ |date=20181207175229 }}. ''The Express Tribune''. 18 April 2016.</ref>

2006年9月5日，巴基斯坦與瓦济里斯坦伊斯兰酋长国部落领袖签署《瓦济里斯坦协议》，結束瓦济里斯坦戰爭。<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=BksqAQAAIAAJ|title=South Asia Defence and Strategic Year Book|publisher=Panchsheel|year=2009|page=260|access-date=2021-09-10|archive-date=2021-09-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210910071219/https://books.google.com/books?id=BksqAQAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 北瓦济里斯坦特区 ==
[[北瓦济里斯坦特区|北瓦济里斯坦特区]]的首府設在米蘭夏(Miramshah)。 當地多山，多部落。部落多為[[普什圖人|普什圖人]]。<ref name=":1" />

== 南瓦济里斯坦特区 ==
[[南瓦济里斯坦特区|南瓦济里斯坦特区]]的首府设在[[瓦納_(巴基斯坦)|瓦納]]，面积约6500平方公里，是巴基斯坦最不稳定的行政區之一。南瓦济里斯坦特区不是由[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]政府直接管轄，而是委由當地自治。<ref name=":1" />

